I want to thank @chrisallmeid @obislet_ @lorenzoclicks @shotdown_doc and everyone that purchased a shirt, or supported us in any way during our BETA stage. 

This shirt was made with the idea of representing
myself as a multi-faceted creator & photographer in public. I always knew the way you represent yourself is more important than the service you provide. That is why I created this. To help creators get their point across without having to speak too much. I wear this shirt every chance I get because it brings me new business. Everywhere I go people stop me to ask me if I’m a photographer and to get my contact. That’s how I knew it works for me. And I hope it does the same for you.
